{"_id":"1163b6f7-61ef-4fcb-ace2-4329231fda81","type":"Item","name":"Leadership 1: Public Speaking","system":{"skill":"Leadership","name":"Public Speaking","rank":"1","type":"ability","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"","description":"Whenever you need to sway a group of non-hostile people toward your point of view or convince them to take some course of action, you gain a Boon.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"11bed361-fbe2-4cd7-9739-0a394b7fd341","type":"Item","name":"Leadership 1: Inspiration","system":{"skill":"Leadership","name":"Inspiration","rank":"1","type":"technique","speed":"fast","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You grant an ally a Boon on the next check they make.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"2898cdd6-498c-4964-b3dc-c1609294faa5","type":"Item","name":"Leadership 5: No One Left Behind","system":{"skill":"Leadership","name":"No One Left Behind","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"reaction","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"1","description":"This may be used once per combat when an ally takes damage that would inflict a Wound. Reduce the damage by the result of your check, or by double that amount if the original damage would leave them critically wounded.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"2ad3b1a3-9b35-4f44-8137-c2d41fa01336","type":"Item","name":"Leadership 1: Planning Stages","system":{"skill":"Leadership","name":"Planning Stages","rank":"1","type":"activity","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"","description":"At the beginning of a Venture, or at the beginning of a new day, you may spend an hour going over possible plans and contingencies with your party. Each ally that participate in the strategizing gains one Leadership Point, which can be used during that Venture to reroll a failed check.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"56ba9246-6f3e-4b3d-bae7-632c30dfede6","type":"Item","name":"Leadership 5: Rally the Troops","system":{"skill":"Leadership","name":"Rally the Troops","rank":"5","type":"activity","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"","description":"You may attempt to rally your allies once at the end of the day. They (and you) regain an additional Endurance when sleeping. If the Consequence Tracker has a positive value, you may make a check against level 3 (roll 6 or higher). On a success, remove a Consequence from the tracker.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"8b242b90-f63c-4ccc-9e77-52108c12b5d1","type":"Item","name":"Leadership 5: Follower","system":{"skill":"Leadership","name":"Follower","rank":"5","type":"ability","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"","description":"You gain a Level 3 Companion. They are a person with three skills of your choice and no special abilities. If they die they may be replaced during down time between Ventures.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"8ea2171b-e5ee-45d1-962f-28cd9d3ee3d7","type":"Item","name":"Leadership 3: Fearless Leader","system":{"skill":"Leadership","name":"Fearless Leader","rank":"3","type":"technique","speed":"reaction","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"2","description":"This may be used once per combat when you take damage that would inflict a Major or Critical Wound. Reduce the damage by the result of your check. If this reduces the severity of the wound, your allies gain a Boon on all checks for the duration of the combat or until you take another Major or Critical Wound.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"c4a14cb7-69b2-4454-9715-ffdc9433e4c1","type":"Item","name":"Leadership 3: Delegator","system":{"skill":"Leadership","name":"Delegator","rank":"3","type":"ability","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"2","description":"Whenever you and your party must all roll to complete tasks that take more than one round (such as when you each contribute to setting up camp in your own way or when you all make checks to traverse some hazard) you may make a Leadership check. After all your allies have made their rolls, divide the result of your check among their results as you wish. For example, if you and your allies rolled 8, 5, 4, and 3, and your Leadership check was a 6, you might add 3 points to the 3, 2 points to the 4, and 1 point to the 5 to bring them all to 6.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"d5681073-d505-464d-9397-c46f32e2fdcf","type":"Item","name":"Leadership 3: Coordinated Assault","system":{"skill":"Leadership","name":"Coordinated Assault","rank":"3","type":"ability","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"2","description":"In combat, you can allow an ally to act during your turn, taking your actions and movements in any order. They gain a Boon to all checks they make when doing so. They skip their next turn.","domain":"Expertise","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
